# Luxe — Premium Ecommerce Project Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete full-stack premium ecommerce store — **Luxe** — with a luxury aesthetic inspired by Kimirica/Nykaa Luxe.

---

## Frontend (React + Vite)

### Design System
- **CSS custom properties** for all color tokens, spacing, typography, shadows, animations
- **Colors**: Background `#EAF1FF`, Primary `#1A1A2E` (navy), Accent `#B8860B` (gold)
- **Fonts**: Playfair Display (headings, serif, italic) + Inter (body, sans-serif) via Google Fonts
- **Global animations**: fadeInUp, fadeIn, slideIn, scaleIn, shimmer (skeleton loading)

### Pages Built (10 total)
| Page | Route | Features |
|------|-------|---------|
| HomePage | `/` | Hero, CategoryGrid, Featured Products, Promo Banner, Best Sellers, USP Strip, Newsletter |
| ProductsPage | `/products` | Sidebar filter (category, price range), sort, search, grid/list view |
| ProductDetailPage | `/products/:slug` | Image gallery, rating stars, qty control, add-to-cart, wishlist, tabs, reviews, related |
| CartPage | `/cart` | Items list, qty control, order summary (subtotal+tax+shipping), coupon input |
| CheckoutPage | `/checkout` | 4-step: Address → Shipping → Payment (Stripe) → Review |
| LoginPage | `/login` | Email+password, show/hide password, error toast |
| RegisterPage | `/register` | Name+email+password+confirm, validation |
| DashboardPage | `/dashboard` | Profile edit, order history, saved addresses |
| OrderConfirmationPage | `/order-confirmation/:id` | Success animation, order ID, status steps |
| AdminPage | `/admin` | Sidebar nav, stats dashboard, products CRUD table, orders management |

### Components Built
- **Navbar** — sticky, backdrop-blur, hide-on-scroll-down, 3-column grid (search | logo | icons), mobile hamburger menu
- **CartSidebar** — slide-in drawer with items, qty, subtotal, checkout link
- **HeroSection** — full-viewport background image, dark overlay, serif headline, dual CTA
- **CategoryGrid** — 4 clickable cards with image zoom + gradient overlay on hover
- **ProductCard** — dual-image hover swap, badges (NEW/SALE), add-to-cart, quick view
- **Footer** — dark premium, social icons, newsletter subscribe, multi-column nav

### State Management
- **CartContext** — useReducer with localStorage persistence, add/remove/updateQty/clear
- **AuthContext** — JWT token management, axios header injection, login/register/logout

