## How to Run

```bash
# Terminal 1 — Frontend
cd frontend
npm run dev     → http://localhost:5173

# Terminal 2 — Backend (after filling .env)
cd backend
npm run dev     → http://localhost:5000

# Seed sample data
cd backend
node seeds/seed.js
```

